** AERMOD Control Pathway
****************************************
CO STARTING
   TITLEONE BG Test Run
   TITLETWO NO2 with Background
   MODELOPT NOCHKD CONC TTRM ALPHA
   AVERTIME 1
   POLLUTID NO2
