**   EMISUNIT 1.0E3 GRAMS/SEC MILLIGRAMS/M**3
   SRCGROUP ALL      BACKGROUND
   SRCGROUP BACKGRND BACKGROUND
   SRCGROUP SRCSS 01
SO FINISHED

****************************************
** AERMOD Receptor Pathway
****************************************
RE STARTING
   GRIDPOLR POL1 STA
   GRIDPOLR POL1 ORIG 0 0
   GRIDPOLR POL1 DIST 10 100
   GRIDPOLR POL1 GDIR 36 10 10
   GRIDPOLR POL1 END
RE FINISHED

****************************************
** AERMOD Meteorology Pathway
****************************************
